column1: #   This CSV file maps NEF v1.0  tags to NMR-STAR v3.2.0.1
#   The software specific data i.e tags and data which are not part of the standard NEF v1.0 dictionary will be stored in Details tag in relevant saveframes in NMR-STAR as a text block.
#   Second Column : NMR-STAR saveframe/loop/tag (author tags i.e data copied from a NEF tag goes here ; example : HBx)
#   Third Column : NMR-STAR saveframe/loop/tag (tanslated data goes here ; example HB2)
